name: COVID19ICD10CMValueSetForLungCancerAll
title: COVID19 ICD10CM Value Set for Lung Cancer, All
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of values contains terms related to lung cancer.),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes primary and secondary lung cancer as well as cancer metastatic to the lungs. It includes non-small cell and small cell lung cancers as well as lung adenoid cystic carcinoma, carcinoid tumors, lymphomas, and sarcomas.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes benign neoplasms, carcinoma in situ, lung neoplasms of uncertain behavior, lung cancer in remission, personal and/or family history of lung cancer, and complications due to lung cancer.)
